<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="row mb-4">
  <div class="col-md-12">
    <h1 class="mb-4">Our Services</h1>
    <p class="lead">Discover our range of professional massage therapy services designed to meet your wellness needs.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row mb-5">
  <% if (services && services.length > 0) { %>
    <% services.forEach(service => { %>
      <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
        <div class="card h-100">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title h4"><%= service.name %></h2>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-3">
              <span class="badge bg-primary rounded-pill"><%= service.duration %> minutes</span>
              <span class="text-primary fw-bold">$<%= service.price %></span>
            </div>
            <p class="card-text"><%= service.description %></p>
            <div class="d-grid">
              <a href="/booking?service=<%= service.id %>" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Book This Service</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% }) %>
  <% } else { %>
    <div class="col-12 text-center">
      <p>No services available at the moment. Please check back later.</p>
    </div>
  <% } %>
</div>

<div class="row mb-5">
  <div class="col-md-12">
    <div class="card bg-light">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title h4 text-center mb-4">Massage Benefits</h2>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
            <div class="text-center">
              <i class="bi bi-heart fs-1 text-primary mb-3"></i>
              <h3 class="h5">Stress Reduction</h3>
              <p>Massage therapy helps reduce stress hormones and promotes relaxation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
            <div class="text-center">
              <i class="bi bi-activity fs-1 text-primary mb-3"></i>
              <h3 class="h5">Pain Relief</h3>
              <p>Alleviates muscle tension and chronic pain conditions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
            <div class="text-center">
              <i class="bi bi-droplet fs-1 text-primary mb-3"></i>
              <h3 class="h5">Improved Circulation</h3>
              <p>Enhances blood flow and promotes better nutrient delivery to tissues.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row mb-5">
  <div class="col-md-12">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title h4 text-center mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h3 class="accordion-header">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq1">
                What should I expect during my first massage?
              </button>
            </h3>
            <div id="faq1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                During your first visit, you'll complete a brief health history form. Your massage therapist will discuss your goals and any areas of concern. You'll then be left to undress to your comfort level and lie on the massage table under the sheet. The therapist will knock before re-entering, and only the area being worked on will be uncovered.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h3 class="accordion-header">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq2">
                How often should I get a massage?
              </button>
            </h3>
            <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                The frequency depends on your individual needs and goals. For general wellness and stress management, once a month is common. For addressing specific issues or chronic pain, weekly or bi-weekly sessions may be recommended. Your therapist can help determine the best schedule for you.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq-3">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-collapse-3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-collapse-3">
                What's the difference between the massage types?
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="faq-collapse-3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq-3" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Foot massage focuses on relieving tension through the feet's pressure points. Body massage provides full-body relaxation and tension relief. Combo massage offers the best of both worlds with a foot massage followed by a body massage. The duration you choose depends on your needs and time availability. Our therapists can recommend the best option for you.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h3 class="accordion-header">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq4">
                Should I avoid eating before a massage?
              </button>
            </h3>
            <div id="faq4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                It's best not to eat a heavy meal right before your massage, but you shouldn't arrive hungry either. A light meal or snack 1-2 hours before your appointment is ideal. Stay hydrated by drinking water before and after your session.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
